ngModel is a two way banding function in angular.

set up a ngModel for your angular:
    1. go to angular.module.ts file
    2. import import { FormsModule } from "@angular/Forms";
    3. add FormsModule into imports

now you can use ngModule in your tamplate html.
    EXAMPLE:
        <input [(ngModule)] = "user.firstName" type="text">

        EXPLAN:
            [] this is bind data from component to template,
            () this is for event, it bind data from template to component to class.
            [()] this is two way binding